{"tid":278232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你嘅生理時鐘宜家幾點？","createTime":"2017-06-10T09:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T09:51:34.000Z","uid":101367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8cee1dd78de39eae6b7b7da205d5f55eddf1ef","tid":278232,"uid":101367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"早幾日開始失眠 今朝五點幾都未訓 個胃開始痛就求其食咗塊餅 係張床碌咗好耐先訓到<br />\n啲人成日話幾點要訓覺 又話身體啲器官幾點係要排毒 唔知幾點又話要休息 心諗 我點知我生理時鐘幾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我連訓都訓唔到喎<br />\n其實有無咩辦法知道自己生理時鐘係幾點？<br />\n<br />\n好似有啲膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e3e927babb18f6d9150dd955e615786bfc4be5","tid":278232,"uid":74190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:51:34.000Z","msg":"以為你問緊心理時鍾巴打而家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}